{
  "stem": "24884.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in the neighborhood of the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [GERMAN], I think.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] For-- we-- we moved around quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know for what reason.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember 1, 2, 3 different places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ordinary apartments.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at one point, the last one, my mother had to-- the rents were very expensive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she didn't have the income like that anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she rented out two or three rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Besides, it was also a fact that Jews were not allowed to have an apartment for themselves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to share.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I think it was in school, from one of my teachers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think that was it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a known-- known fact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you-- you-- it was-- it was forced antisemitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was told.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People have been told the Jews are this and the Jews are that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you were not so much aware of being different in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You were much more assimilated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And suddenly, you were a different person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was only that one teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the others were pretty nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And especially our principal was a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was at a point, I think, the last Jewish girl in school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he always try to keep me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said-- I remember once he said to me, Mendel, I want you to finish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want you to be able to have an education.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I will try not to report-- they had to report.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I will try not to report as long as I can possibly do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That's all what I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
